    <h1>Audio2 Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: January 2025</p>
    
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>Audio2 does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information. The app operates entirely on your device.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Usage</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Podcast content is streamed directly from public RSS feeds</li>
        <li>Generated videos are saved locally to your iOS Photos app</li>
        <li>No user accounts, analytics, or tracking</li>
        <li>No data is sent to our servers</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Third-Party Content</h2>
    <p>Audio2 accesses publicly available podcast RSS feeds. All podcast content belongs to the respective creators.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: [your-email]@gmail.com</p>
    
    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.</p>
